&lt;!--more--&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It is developing on &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;dev&lt;/code&gt; branch, you can run &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;git checkout dev&lt;/code&gt; to switch to this branch.&lt;/p&gt;

